title: American Horror Story: Hotel Soundtrack | 48. Marianne Faithfull - The Ballad of Lucy Jordan
author: American Horror Story Brasil
comment: Both the saddest and happiest endings for an AHS character.
Liz is really the best. A great woman ! Thank you for giving some hope !
The death of Liz is only the death scene that bring me tears

Liz Taylor is the best character ever, played by an outstanding actor. Ad then there is Gaga, and I have not enough enthusiastic words about her performance. She deserved that Globe! Actually they should make a Gaga Barbie Countess after her interpretation of The Queen
description:
EPISODE 5.12 SEASON FINALE -  Be Our Guest

Liz pede aos fantasmas que a ajudem a renascer; Todos pegam uma arma para ajudar Liz quando a Condessa chega e corta a garganta de Liz.  | Liz asks her 'children' to help her be reborn; All the ghosts of the hotel reluctantly grab weapons to help Liz pass over when the Countess arrives - Elizabeth slices Liz's throat.
